postData.title: LockedDimension
postData.contentHtml:
Information

Description: LockedDimension allows you to disable, lock dimensions behind permissions nodes, and much more. all within a single plugin.

Available at: GitHub & Spigot

Details

An incredible plugin, honestly. I had to abandon it last year for personal reasons, unfortunately.

Fun Fact: This wouldn't have existed if MobPreventer didn't get as much attrition as I imagined.
